title: Ep. 187 - REALITY TV REVIEWS
description:
2018 Olympic Bobsled Silver Medalist Lauren Gibbs reviews this week’s episode of Bravo’s Real Housewives of Dallas. 

 

Steve Stauff reviews the Lifetime TV movie Escaping the NXIVM Cult: A Mother’s Fight to Save Her Daughter. 

 

Comedian Chris Franjola reviews the season premiere of Fox’s The Masked Singer.
